# Shell environment

Before running any terminal command in this project, source the work profile first:

```bash
source ~/.zsh-work/.zprofile
```

This ensures the correct Cloudflare API token and other work credentials are loaded (not personal account credentials from the default shell).

For Cloudflare Wrangler commands in this project, also set:

```bash
export CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=880ecf74da02edf846e1a540a835df40
```

Or use `npm run deploy` / `npm run deploy:preview`, which handle both automatically via `scripts/deploy.sh`.
